      <title>甚至在普拉特纳退出之前，民主党人就谁接替他产生了冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/us/politics/graham-platner-maine-replacements-democrats.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[进步派和温和派正准备就缅因州尚未决定的程序展开斗争，以提名一位参议院提名人来接替强奸指控后的格雷厄姆·普拉特纳。他也还想有发言权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/us/politics/graham-platner-maine-replacements-democrats.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 02:26:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国打击伊朗并在油轮袭击后重新实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/us/politics/us-strikes-iran-tanker-attacks.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此次军事行动是在美国财政部撤销允许伊朗石油全球销售的豁免几小时后进行的。]]></description>
