    <item>
      <title>关于曼哈顿中城“冰冻区”的知识</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/nyregion/frozen-zone-midtown-manhattan-building-collapse.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一座面临部分倒塌风险的建筑促使该市限制该地区的行人和车辆通行。部分公交车改道或晚点，但地铁线路并未中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/nyregion/frozen-zone-midtown-manhattan-building-collapse.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:09:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“梁开始弯曲”：曼哈顿中城建筑危险下垂</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/nyregion/midtown-building-collapse-housing-project.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于结构性损坏影响了办公室改建项目，东 42 街周围的办公室和酒店被疏散。该地区的交通已停止。没有人员受伤的报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/nyregion/midtown-building-collapse-housing-project.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 00:06:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着以色列失去美国的支持，拉姆·伊曼纽尔批评内塔尼亚胡</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/us/politics/rahm-emanuel-speech-israel.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这位正在探索 2028 年总统竞选的民主党人、前芝加哥市长在特拉维夫呼吁美国停止对以色列的无条件支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/us/politics/rahm-emanuel-speech-israel.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 23:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市中心为酒店客人疏散紧急计划</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/travel/midtown-hotels-building-collapse.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这座不稳定建筑附近至少两家酒店已被疏散，导致旅客滞留，迫使客人爬上其他住所。]]></description>
